headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Overflod Tyrant & Vapid Dominator GTX
content: This week brings a new dilemma to the car connoisseurs of Los Santos. On the one hand a svelte, sophisticated bombshell made as only the Swedish know how. And on the other, something that’s half brute force, half pristine performance and all American. But of course, it’s only a dilemma if you only pick one...
